a user's account is divided between 3 tables: usersTable, accountsTable, and either freelancersTable or EmployersTable based on if the user is a freelancer or an employer.

The freelancer account contains the following information

first_name
last_name
email
country
address
region
phone
website_url
social_media_links
about (text)
fields_of_expertise (text[])
portfolio (jsonb: {
  projectName: string
  projectLink: string
  projectDescription: string
  attachmentId?: number
  projectImageName?: string
  projectImageUrl?: string
}[])
work_history (jsonb: {
  title: string
  company: string
  currentlyWorkingThere: boolean
  startDate: Date | string
  endDate: Date | string
  jobDescription: string
}[])
cv_link
video_link
certificates (jsonb: {
  certificateName: string
  issuedBy: string
  yearIssued: number
  attachmentId?: number
  attachmentName?: string
  attachmentUrl?: string
}[])
educations (jsonb:{
  degree: string
  field: string
  institution: string
  completedOn: string
}[]),
years_of_experience
preferred_project_types
hourly_rate
compensation_type
available_for_work (boolean)
available_from (date)
jobs_open_to
hoursAvailableFrom
hoursAvailableTo

